{"word":"G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o - Anoint","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chríō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khree'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Anoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அபிஷேகம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. consecrating Jesus to the Messianic office"},{"paragraph":"2. enduing Christians with the gifts of the Holy Spirit"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5530 - χράομαι - chráomai - khrah'-om-ahee/5530\">G5530</a> through the idea of <i>contact</i>; to <i>smear</i> or <i>rub</i> with oil, that is, (by implication) to <i>consecrate</i> to an office or religious service: - anoint."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G500 - ἀντίχριστος - antíchristos - an-tee'-khris-tos/500\">G500</a>, <a href=\"#/G5545 - χρῖσμα - chrîsma - khris'-mah/5545\">G5545</a>, <a href=\"#/G5546 - Χριστιανός - Christianós - khris-tee-an-os'/5546\">G5546</a>, <a href=\"#/G5547 - Χριστός - Christós - khris-tos'/5547\">G5547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5548 - χρίω - chríō - khree'-o/5548\">G5548</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580 - ψευδόχριστος - pseudóchristos - psyoo-dokh'-ris-tos/5580\">G5580</a>"}]}